xercise.", "bbox": [150.0, 867.1, 697.7, 888.1]}, {"text": "• Expected dividend yield of 1.68 percent, 1.30 percent, and 1.57 percent, respectively, based on the dividend rate at the date of grant.", "bbox": [150.0, 896.3, 1163.3, 917.3]}, {"text": "• \u0007Risk free interest rate of 1.89 percent, 2.93 percent, and 4.67 percent, respectively, based on the yield of treasury bonds at the date", "bbox": [150.0, 925.5, 1152.6, 946.4]}, {"text": "of grant.", "bbox": [160.0, 954.6, 228.6, 975.6]}, {"text": "ESPP", "bbox": [112.5, 1028.6, 167.4, 1061.2]}, {"text": "ESPP activity is summarized as follows:", "bbox": [150.1, 1071.2, 448.3, 1092.2]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31", "bbox": [854.7, 1112.7, 1025.2, 1131.4]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [790.1, 1137.6, 830.0, 1156.4]}, {"text": "2008", "bbox": [941.4, 1137.7, 980.1, 1156.4]}, {"text": "2007", "bbox": [1091.4, 1137.7, 1125.5, 1156.4]}, {"text": "Number of Shares Sold", "bbox": [112.5, 1169.2, 291.2, 1190.2]}, {"text": "232,962", "bbox": [755.8, 1169.1, 835.8, 1190.2]}, {"text": "148,490", "bbox": [908.2, 1169.2, 985.9, 1190.2]}, {"text": "114,420", "bbox": [1058.3, 1169.2, 1130.7, 1190.2]}, {"text": "Weighted Average Exercise Price", "bbox": [112.5, 1198.4, 365.5, 1219.4]}, {"text": "$14.94", "bbox": [765.9, 1198.3, 835.8, 1219.4]}, {"text": "$20.44", "bbox": [917.9, 1198.4, 985.9, 1219.4]}, {"text": "$24.32", "bbox": [1068.0, 1198.4, 1130.7, 1219.4]}, {"text": "Weighted Average Grant Date Fair Value", "bbox": [112.5, 1227.6, 423.3, 1248.6]}, {"text": "$  4.13", "bbox": [765.9, 1227.5, 835.8, 1248.6]}, {"text": "$  5.72", "bbox": [917.9, 1227.6, 985.9, 1248.6]}, {"text": "$  5.18", "bbox": [1068.0, 1227.6, 1125.5, 1248.6]}]}